public class FilterAllRDFTypes<T extends com.hp.hpl.jena.rdf.model.RDFNode>
extends com.hp.hpl.jena.util.iterator.Filter<T>

FilterAllRDFTypes This filter accepts elements that have ALL RDF Types it is looking for. When used for keeping, it will keep any instances of ALL types contemplated When used for dropping, it will drop those elements that are instances of SOME of the types contemplated
